Document Purpose: DEMISSION - APPOINTMENT - CESSION OF SOCIAL PARTS
Summary: The Assembly successively took up all the items on the agenda and, after deliberate action, adopted the following resolutions. The above resolutions were adopted successively by unanimity. The resignation of Mr. EL AKILI IDRISS from his position as manager, which dates from today. The appointment of Mr EL AKili IMAD as Director at this date and for an indefinite period.
